OL,3,CNatalie McNally murder 'planned,
OL,4,Ccalculated and pre-meditated,' court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe murder of a pregnant woman in Co
OL,8,FArmagh has been described as "planned,
OL,9,Fcalculated and pre-meditated".
OL,11,FNatalie McNally, 32, was 15 weeks
OL,12,Fpregnant when she was attacked in her
OL,13,Fhome in Lurgan a week before Christmas
OL,14,Fin 2022.
OL,16,FStephen McCullagh, 36, of Woodland
OL,17,FGardens, Lisburn, has denied her
OL,18,Fmurder.
OL,26,@pD@^OUqD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
