FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1771970741
OL,3,CNatalie McNally murder 'planned,
OL,4,Ccalculated and pre-meditated,' court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FHe sat in the dock at Belfast Crown
OL,8,FCourt between two prison guards on
OL,9,FMonday morning as the trial opened.
OL,11,FA jury of six men and six women have
OL,12,Fbeen sworn to serve during the trial,
OL,13,Fwhich is expected to last for around
OL,14,Ffive weeks, before Judge Mr Justice
OL,15,FPatrick Kinney.
OL,17,FProsecuting barrister Charles
OL,18,FMacCreanor KC said it is their case
OL,19,Fthat the defendant murdered Ms McNally
OL,20,Fand then "put on an act" to cover his
OL,21,Ftracks.
OL,26,@|D@JOU|D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
