PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1771970741
OL,3,CNatalie McNally murder 'planned,
OL,4,Ccalculated and pre-meditated,' court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"We say that this is a planned,
OL,8,Fcalculated, pre-meditated murder by
OL,9,Fthe defendant," he said.
OL,11,F"One which he hoped to get away with.
OL,13,F"Natalie McNally had suffered serious
OL,14,Fand multiple fatal injuries."
OL,16,FHe said her cause of death was found
OL,17,Fto have involved compression of her
OL,18,Fneck, "suggestive of finger tips
OL,19,Fgrasping".
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@OO]sD@AOUuD@AOUvD@]O]zD@GOU{D@
OL,26,AIO]
