PN,44704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1771970741
OL,3,CNatalie McNally murder 'planned,
OL,4,Ccalculated and pre-meditated,' court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FShe also suffered three stab wounds to
OL,8,Fher neck caused by a bladed weapon and
OL,9,Ffive lacerations to the back, top and
OL,10,Fright of her head "in keeping with
OL,11,Fhaving sustained at least five heavy
OL,12,Fblows".
OL,14,FHe said any of these could have caused
OL,15,Fdeath alone.
OL,17,FHe went on: "Natalie McNally was
OL,18,Fpregnant at the time and Stephen
OL,19,FMcCullagh was the father of her unborn
OL,20,Fchild."
OL,26,@rD@SOUtD@FO]yD@MOU|D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
