OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1771970741
OL,3,CNatalie McNally murder 'planned,
OL,4,Ccalculated and pre-meditated,' court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe time of death has been estimated
OL,8,Fto be between 8.50pm and 9.30pm on
OL,9,FSunday December 18 2022.
OL,11,FMcCullagh made a 999 call at around
OL,12,F10pm on Monday December 19 from her
OL,13,Fhome in Lurgan.
OL,15,F"On the prosecution case, this call is
OL,16,Ffalse, it's an act, it's put on by
OL,17,Fhim, part of his plan to do the murder
OL,18,Fand get away with it," Mr MacCreanor
OL,19,FKC said.
OL,26,@wD@AOUzD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
