PN,44706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1771970741
OL,3,CNatalie McNally murder 'planned,
OL,4,Ccalculated and pre-meditated,' court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FHe said the ambulance service and
OL,8,Fpolice were quickly at the scene, and
OL,9,Freported finding McCullagh with Ms
OL,10,FMcNally.
OL,12,F"Natalie McNally is lying at the top
OL,13,Fof the stairs ... which was the living
OL,14,Farea of the home," he said.
OL,16,F"It's clearly apparent to paramedics
OL,17,Fthat Natalie McNally is dead,
OL,18,Feverything is consistent with this
OL,19,Fbeing an attack upon her, presence of
OL,20,Fblood and the visible injuries.
OL,26,@tD@AOUvD@RO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
