CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1771970741
OL,3,CNatalie McNally murder 'planned,
OL,4,Ccalculated and pre-meditated,' court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"Stephen McCullagh is described by the
OL,8,Fparamedics as performing CPR to the
OL,9,Ffemale and he's described as being
OL,10,Fquite visibly upset."
OL,12,FHe said police described McCullagh as
OL,13,Fbeing "distraught and overcome".
OL,15,F"Again, we say this is all part of an
OL,16,Fact, a front," he said.
